  policy, then you apply the firewall policy to a firewall. Network Firewall acts as a proxy
  service to decrypt and inspect the traffic traveling through your firewalls. You can
  reference a TLS inspection configuration from more than one firewall policy, and you can
  use a firewall policy in more than one firewall. For more information about using TLS
